race.comment: FLYING PROUD (2) missed the frame two back but wound up strongly last time, finishing on late when second (34.72) in a Grade 4/5 at The Meadows. Has a good record at this journey. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature in the finish again. FADE TO BLACK (1) is a well performed dog and winner of 13 races who was in the minor money last time out at Shepparton (37.69). Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to feature again. ASTON PRATT (3) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at The Meadows in a handy 34.63 beating FLYING PROUD. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Must be included in calculations. PAW HELION (7) cannot be underestimated.
